headline: Wells Fargo Bank Decreases Prime Rate to 7.50 Percent
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, December 18, 2024--Wells Fargo Bank, N.A., said today it is decreasing its prime rate to 7.50 percent from 7.75 percent, effective tomorrow, Dec. 19, 2024.
